{"tid":609421,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連囝要唔要考慮整頓一下連登風氣","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T04:48:32.000Z","uid":82829,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"516daa0b7d7f067b267e6a59c665af00e51a2e5c","tid":609421,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"而家嘅連登質素的確係每況愈下<br />\n喺會員質素上面絕對反映到<br />\n唔講高登個時咁遠啦，淨係講連登啱啱開個陣<br />\n個時啲絲打影相影到自己對腳<br />\n點都會有班人走出嚟屌佢借啲影腳收兵<br />\n而家已經冇人屌啦<br />\n<br />\n好似呢個po咁<br />\n<em>我係絲 有無人想睇我露波</em><br />\n<em><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/605515/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/605515/page/1</a></em><br />\n入面條女影完都冇人屌<br />\n仲要引嚟班厹話貼多啲貼多啲<br />\n<br />\n根本上而家嘅連登你話係一個交配論壇都唔過份<br />\n<br />\n呢個po仲過份<br />\n<em>絲打一人n個無意間被挑逗到嘅情況</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/598762/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/598762/page/2</a><br />\n本來個po好地地<br />\n後來有人講到MTR上面(唔覺意)抽水嘅情況<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就被人騎劫<br />\n騎劫個班人甚至開埋個新po繼續<br />\n<br />\n<em>日日都好想傾....計(3)</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/607456/page/3\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/607456/page/3</a><br />\n入面條女同班厹傾淫嘢西痕到甚至出嚟玩MTR抽水play<br />\n<br />\n你話我舉出嚟嘅都係成人台嘅po<br />\n講啲咁嘅嘢有乜出奇<br />\n其實成人台本身只係畀班咸濕仔交流咸片咸網嘅平台<br />\n點估到會被人當係5p , 交友app咁用<br />\n<br />\n去到錯別字<br />\n留意到班會員都唔知係盲反定係點<br />\n一見到肥絲就屌<br />\n呢到有個po我覺得個觀點同我好似<br />\n<br />\n<em>請會員肥絲大隻入嚟</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/607872/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/607872/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>雖然好多人唔鍾意你 因為你嗰種捉字方法<br />\n但先唔討論你個方法討唔討人歡喜<br />\n我係真心想請你粵語正字<br />\n眼見愈嚟愈多人打埋囇啲「左」「d」<br />\n明明一直都會俾其他人屌老母<br />\n而家就個個掛住反鳩你 而已經冇人再打啱啲字<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n佢都講咗好多我想講嘅嘢就唔多講啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個po真係睇到幾心寒<br />\n<em>所以依家連登係咪同祖國接軌？屌人寫殘體係錯？</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/609347/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/609347/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/112433_69f1480c4d493f5e37fa8f33bb59a630.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F112433_69f1480c4d493f5e37fa8f33bb59a630.png&h=a7c4fcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百五個comment繼後都無人屌無人發現，發現左仲要俾人串串貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多都預咗被人負皮甚至冇人理<br />\n喺到引用返LIHKG第一個post嘅其中一句<br />\n<em>LIHKG 討論區正式成立 🎊 新世代，新平台，新開始</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote>會員就係討論區嘅核心，我地一定會接受同跟進大家嘅意見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連囝係真心想整好個論壇嘅就應該認真考慮下<br />\n會員質素反映論壇質素<br />\n如果你係諗住借連登搵$$搵夠就收檔嘅可以無視我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c50a05be9a3ba2266e97ad541b5a76b0afa609","tid":609421,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d23d479c3fb9336b63a7673835c61c23f40fa62b","tid":609421,"uid":21819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"咁你收檔啦"}]}